    public class AddJDBCDriverOperator
extends NbDialogOperator
    Handles "New JDBC Driver" dialog.
    Usage: 
          DriversNode.invoke().addDriver();
      AddJDBCDriverOperator addDlgOperator = new AddJDBCDriverOperator();
      addDlgOperator.add();
      ...
      addDlgOperator.ok();
